      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>A bill to include sexual assault and aggravated sexual violence in the definition of aggravated felonies under the Immigration and Nationality Act in order to expedite the removal of aliens convicted of such crimes.</title>
